Use this file when handing off one experiment cell to an agent.

One experiment cell means:
- one `prompt_id`
- one `run_profile_id`
- one `condition`

There are two agent roles:
- `response agent` for `baseline`, `prompted`, `critique_initial`, and `critique_revised`
